               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa ʾAbrǝham “Book of Abraham” (fols. 3r-28vb), incomplete,
                     inidentified
 II) Taʾammǝra Śǝllāse “Miracles of the Trinity”: 7 miracles
                     (fols. 29ra-45vb), incomplete.</summary>
