                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. is worn and shows traces of intensive
                           use.
 The back board is missing; the Ms. was possibly rebound.
                           Many fols. seem to be missing or are misplaced. 
 Ink faded or
                           abraded on <locus target="#4v">4v</locus>, 7r, 15r, 25r, 26r, 27v,
                           28v.
 Some fols. are damaged with text loss, <locus target="#42">42</locus>, 44, 45.</condition>
