               <provenance>The names of the original donors have been
                     erased on 3ra, 5vb, 18vb, 21rb. ʾAbuna Walda Rufāʾel is mentioned in the
                     supplication formula on 40vb. The Ms. is owned by the church of Gabra
                     Manfas Qǝddus ʿOna Maʿḍo.</provenance></history>
